    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean by \"letting go\"? everything feels so pointless. i look at his side of the bed and i just feel this massive, crushing weight. it's like there's no reason to keep trying to fill a space that's meant for him. it feels more like a burden than a life at this point.",
